==迭事==
2013年6月，一個國際性酒店及機票訂購網站將赤柱正灘評為「全球十佳沙灘」的第十位<ref>{{cite news |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130608/18289254 |title=赤柱泳灘入全球10大 |date=2013-06-08 |accessdate=2013-06-08 |publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]] |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2015-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702160742/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130608/18289254 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cheapflights.com/news/top-10-city-beaches-around-the-world |title=Top 10 city beaches around the world |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-08 |publisher=CheapFlights Travel Blog |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310122816/https://www.cheapflights.com/news/top-10-city-beaches-around-the-world |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

